no。」「因為電腦及網絡實務最重要係誠信、安全，如果唔係，就好似國泰航空咁，泄漏資料俾人囉。」<br />\n<br />\n睇落讀完可以做IT,  對答又似正常人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ffc457163e8ee330c012423ba762d6caaf62db","tid":935990,"uid":164799,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"佢係咪真係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7add33ffd369b6817c592c609918a05c8ae32192","tid":935990,"uid":93986,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n清醒過正常港豬廢老廢青"},{"pid":"b2471969c5f962616a7c6223bfda6e5bc7bea678","tid":935990,"uid":14449,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"咁都叫弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自閉就可能信"},{"pid":"ee2e50747b7ba88231543611c9bc31292209c4c5","tid":935990,"uid":66943,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9a80bcf5f7f68c4e4607f7c827c23e4647b86c89","tid":935990,"uid":79353,"like":265,"dislike":5,"score":260,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"點解我覺得佢講野仲有point 正常過我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"去check下智商"},{"pid":"5e5cbb0a59fac570c1c48c3b851f0a33e7fbb696","tid":935990,"uid":187493,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a80bcf5f7f68c4e4607f7c827c23e4647b86c89","tid":935990,"uid":79353,"like":265,"dislike":5,"score":260,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"點解我覺得佢講野仲有point 正常過我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201